717756f-a.text:
Broadway, east side, south from West 158th to 156th Streets, showing prominently the 10-story Columbus Apartments at the S.E. corner of 157th Street. Also note at that point, a subway station entrance.
About 1914.

715686f-a.text:
557 West 156th Street, adjoining the N.E. corner of Broadway. This is a three-story frame house.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum fo the City of New York.
Negative No. 590.
